                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/958</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Silliman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Querétaro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-01-05T11:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 5, 1916, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s December 28, 11 a.m. Mining taxes. Subsecretary informed me this
                    morning Chief Executive is disposed to reconsider and reform present mining
                    decree granting interests a considerable reduction. He awaits the arrival here
                    of Cabrera in order to finally formulate the modifications.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Silliman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
